title: The Future's Dust "Drag" - Converse Rubber Tracks: Track of the Week
description:
The single "Drag" by The Future's Dust is this week's "Track of the Week". Recorded at the Converse Rubber Tracks studio in Amsterdam, the five members of the band entered the studio and jumped right into learning about the equipment that was available to them to record their original track. Hear how the band came together and watch them record the single "Drag" at Converse Rubber Tracks in Amsterdam.

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks, check out:
www.converse.com/rubbertracks
